    <item>
      <title>英国脱欧英国放弃了成为全球交易警察的野心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-03-21/brexit-britain-abandons-ambition-to-be-global-deal-cop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国不再想成为全球反托拉斯十字军。改革可能会看到更少的交易被烘烤。这对银行家有好处，为律师而中等，为消费者担心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-03-21/brexit-britain-abandons-ambition-to-be-global-deal-cop</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 05:00:37 GMT</pubDate>
